name: Bust-A-Move 2 - Arcade Edition [GB]
description:
Bust-A-Move 2: Arcade Edition is an arcade game developed by Taito. It came out on 01-01-1996. Acclaim Entertainment published the game. The game is rated as "Recommended" on RAWG.
Bust-A-Move 2: Arcade Edition is available on PC and Nintendo 64.
